scripts.browser: tsc --target es5 --outDir es5 && browserify es5/fcal.js --standalone fcal -o  dist/fcal.js -p common-shakeify  -p bundle-collapser/plugin && uglifyjs --compress --mangle -- dist/fcal.js > dist/fcal.min.js && rm -rf es5
scripts.prepare: npm run build && npm run browser
scripts.version: npm run format && git add -A src
